Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:33.30,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}If I become normal, can I stay close?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:38.79,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}With the children, we link our arms
